@jimma @soul2zimate Is the second part of this comment ("is not supposed ... to be called from deployments") correct?
If so it would be good to clarify that and expand the comment to explain that the accessClassInPackage permission is also needed for that call. That's assuming that is the case.
If tests need weird permissions its good to be very clear on how it's the deployment that needs the perms and not the server code.

